removeInvalidTrussElements

public void removeInvalidTrussElements(Node node)
This method removes invalid elements for example A bar must be attached to 2 nodes A load must be attached to 1 node A Support must be attached to 1 node If any of these requiments are not met the element is removed

removeInvalidTrussElements

public void removeInvalidTrussElements()
This method removes invalid elements for example

  • A bar must be attached to 2 nodes
  • A load must be attached to 1 node
  • A Support must be attached to 1 node

If any of these requiments are not met the element is removed
